Fail explicitly for SSH detach operations that need a live process snapshot.

AgentOS can spawn exec-only child programs, but it cannot clone the V8/WASM
continuation, heap, authenticated transport, channel table, and pending packet
state of a running SSH client. Report this architecture boundary at the exact
detach operation instead of falling through to a generic fork/daemon error or
partially mutating interactive state.

